messages.text: Ada? Are you there? R U O K?
I know you’re upset, but you have to talk to me.
It’s extremely important.
You have to trust me.
I don’t, Christian. I don’t trust anyone right now.
Not even me?
I want to.. but how can I now?
Ada, I can’t emphasize enough how critical it is that you believe what I’m trying to tell you.
Please leave me alone.
I can’t. U know I can’t.
I love you.
Even after what I did?
You didn’t DO anything.
Oh God.. You don’t know yet?
Christian, I’m so sorry. But I swear I had to do it.
I know what you did. And it’s ok.
You HAVE to believe I had no choice.
He was lying to me.
He tried to kidnap me..
I had to do it.
Ada, it’s okay.
I KILLED YOUR DAD, CHRISTIAN… IT’S NOT OKAY!
My dad’s fine, Ada. I promise.
I shot him twice in the chest.
Yes, and he’s thankful you’re a good shot...
but other than some banged up ribs, he’s fine.
What? How?
Think about it, Ada.
He’s a soldier.. going into combat.
God I’m so stupid.
bullet proof vest?
Yup, Kevlar.
Which is worn on the outside BTW
sort of obvious
I wasn’t exactly thinking straight.
I’m just glad u didn’t shoot him in the head.
So he’s really all right?
Yes. And he wasn’t kidnapping you..
I promise..
Why would he kidnap the girl I’m madly in love with? ;)
Do you really mean that?
Of course I do
I can’t believe I’ve waited so long to say it
I love you Ada
Then what was your dad trying to do exactly?
Look - I’ll explain everything later…
right now I need you to listen to me.
We’ve already wasted too much time.
Have you heard from MY dad?
Ada, PLEASE..
just tell me exactly where you are right now.
Sitting on the hood of a stolen car at a rest area in the middle of nowhere.
Where? How far from Austin did you get?
I don’t know. maybe fifty miles.
definitely less than a hundred.
Then PLEASE get in the car and keep driving east – as far away from Austin as possible.
how do you know I’m headed East?
You need to move Ada - NOW
Why? This is a good place to hold up overnight.
Because they’re going to nuke Austin.
What?!
I promise to tell you everything I know
but not until you’re back on the road.
Ada?
ARE U THERE??
What the fuck?
You couldn’t have started by telling me I was about to get nuked?
ARE you driving?
Are you crazy?
Of course I’m driving!
Good. Then stop texting before you wreck.
I just want to hold you in my arms.
Nothing will feel right until that happens.
That’s sweet. I miss you too, C.
But, I have some questions.
OK. I’ll tell you what I know.
At least what you NEED to know right now.
When you’re safe and we’re together, you can ask me anything you want.
OK fine. Go.
First off, I don’t know where your dad is.
I’m sorry
Now, here’s what we know:
Ft. Hood wasn’t the only outbreak.
The Army was working on another strain of the virus down south
at Ft. Sam in San Antonio
They had a breech, just after dark yesterday.
That’s how it reached Austin overnight.
The virus traveled north, not south.
Two outbreaks in two different locations, on the same night…
That can’t be an accident
exactly
But no one is saying who is responsible yet.
What we do know is that this is spreading faster than they can contain it.
So they have no choice but to use nuclear weapons on U.S. soil.
They’re going to wipe out everything south of Waco, Texas..
from the Rio Grande to College Station.
The military wants everyone who is still alive and uninfected to evacuate
and get to Houston ASAP
That’s what I need you to do.
Drive to Houston where we’re waiting for you.
Can you do that for me?
Depends..
Is there anything else you NEED to tell me?
I love you.
So much it hurts.
And maybe don’t text and drive. ☺
Then I guess I’m on my own.
Dad said the world was going to fall apart today
and now I know he was right.
What are you talking about?
You break my heart, Christian.
It’s over.
What’s over?
It seems like everything might be soon…
but you and I are definitely over RIGHT NOW
What are you talking about?
You’re scaring me.
Ada! What are you doing?!
I’m still sitting on the hood of a stolen car at a rest stop on I-10
And I’m wondering
why you thought I was traveling east out of Austin
What?
That’s exactly what my dad told me to do.
But you said you haven’t spoken to him.
So how did you know?
Ada, there’s no time to explain right now.
We’ve been best friends since birth, Christian.
You were my first kiss.
You were the only love I’ve ever known.
Ada, please…
you think I can’t tell when you’re lying?
Especially when it’s so obvious.
SHIT Ada!
there’s no time for this.
You have to trust me
Goodbye, Christian.
At least tell me you’re far away from Austin?!
ADA PLEASE!!!
That’s not your concern.
But Christian
yes?
there is one thing you can do for me
What? Tell me.
I’ll do anything.
Tell your dad that the next time I see him…
I’m shooting him in the head.
